{"tid":2062768,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美議員提《台灣防衞法》阻陸武統","createTime":"2020-06-13T11:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T11:27:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bf8e60e97f3b84f0287e35d97b309c81240d3034","tid":2062768,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:17:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200613/EG6YVWNPKMVITWGLAW7EIAPAWQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200613%2FEG6YVWNPKMVITWGLAW7EIAPAWQ%2F&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJruF5TOcUp1XGW39uuIwQJ%2Fg%3D&h=82c55024\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200613%2FEG6YVWNPKMVITWGLAW7EIAPAWQ%2F&h=822b9bc8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200613/EG6YVWNPKMVITWGLAW7EIAPAWQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n美議員提《台灣防衞法》阻陸武統<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國近年頻以軍事行動威脅台海，美國共和黨籍參議員霍利（Josh Hawley）提出《台灣防衞法》草案（Taiwan Defense Act），以履行《台灣關係法》，維持美軍「阻止中國武力犯台，造成既成事實」能力。台國防部表示，昨日上午發現一架中共運8機進入台西南空域，經台空中偵巡戰機廣播驅趕後，該軍機最終飛離台防空識別區。<br />\n<br />\n提出草案的密蘇里州參議員霍利周四表示，台灣是印太地區自由開放關鍵，若被迫接受統一會威脅到美國與其盟友，「我們絕不能允許這樣的情況發生」。草案要求確保美方有能力履行《台灣關係法》義務，要求國防。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HC5CC4O7UCDF2AHEZFD4LDIM6A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHC5CC4O7UCDF2AHEZFD4LDIM6A.gif&h=7b1b00bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陸軍機昨闖台防空區<br />\n<br />\n此外，台灣中科院周四晚在台東及屏東進行火炮射擊，並試射一枚新型導彈。外界認為這是測試天弓三型增程型防空導彈（圖）。對此，中科院事後指此舉是依據國防。。。。。。。。。。。。。予評論」。對於陸軍昨日又擾台，台國防部強調對台海周邊海空域均能全程監測，目前狀況均正常。<br />\n美聯社"},{"pid":"bbb8b9f2ddce5db04f56cbc0a1fb6cc1fcae6b8a","tid":2062768,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:25:25.000Z","msg":"即係軍事結盟，即係軍事聯防，"},{"pid":"46b3ddca6728e0f51e6b368d405a4e942abaeaff","tid":2062768,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T11:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}